A [[Missions#Other Mission|Mission]] offered at [[stations]].

General difficulty: Moderate 

Same as normal patrol, but this time only killing Xenon. You will also only get paid for killing Xenon ships. 

What you will need: 

* M6/M3 is best. 
* Decent shielding! 
* M1/M2 - with VERY high combat rank and much later on in the game. - by Lord of Nothing 

What you will find: 

* Random Xenon fighters spawning in the specified sector. 
* Kill all of them and you will get paid per Xenon ship killed. 
* Hostile strength increases with combat rank. Expect many M1/M2/M6 class ships much later on! - by Lord of Nothing.


